author: MICHAEL LOSCH Lake Sun Sports Editor mlosch@lakesunonline.com
title: Osage soccer blanked by Sacred Heart
text: Osage soccer blanked by Sacred Heart Comment Posted Oct. 13, 2015 at 5:40 PM By MICHAEL LOSCH mlosch@lakesunonline.com Posted Oct. 13, 2015 at 5:40 PM It was a tough night for Osage on its home pitch Monday night as the Indians were shutout by Sacred Heart 9-0. With the loss, Osage falls to 5-14-1 on the season and will look to rebound with a trip to Richland on Tuesday night before battling in the Stover Tournament over the weekend. By MICHAEL LOSCH
